My Guild </a><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utigerwalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tigerwalker</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_greenspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/17/02 12:40:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouselaboratory.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2282.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Are poisons neccessary?</span><hr size=1> A guildmate of mine...told me that some hi end mobs are only slowable thru rogue poisons. <br>
